#### retrieve channel playlists
```py
from youtubesearchpython import channel

channel = channel("uc_aea8k-eoj3d6gos7hcyng")
print(len(channel.result["playlists"]))
while channel.has_more_playlists():
    channel.next()
    print(len(channel.result["playlists"]))
```

